Casino;;93;;79;;R;;In early-1970s Las Vegas, low-level mobster Sam "Ace" Rothstein (Robert De Niro) gets tapped by his bosses to head the Tangiers Casino. At first, he's a great success in the job, but over the years, problems with his loose-cannon enforcer Nicky Santoro (Joe Pesci), his ex-hustler wife Ginger (Sharon Stone), her con-artist ex Lester Diamond (James Woods) and a handful of corrupt politicians put Sam in ever-increasing danger. Martin Scorsese directs this adaptation of Nicholas Pileggi's book.;;Crime,Drama;;Martin Scorsese;;1995;;Robert De Niro,Sharon Stone,Joe Pesci,James Woods,Don Rickles,Alan King,Kevin Pollak,L.Q. Jones,Dick Smothers,Frank Vincent,Joe Bob Briggs,Pasquale Cajano,Melissa Prophet,Bill Allison,Vinny Vella,Oscar Goodman,Catherine Scorsese,Philip Suriano,Erika von Tagen,Frankie Avalon;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1067987-casino